Description: Extended logging data including HTTP method, URL, client content type, server content type, user agent, referer, x-forwarded-for
The host name of a URL
User login ID detected by the Deep Application Control feature
Source Interface's assigned role (LAN, WAN, etc.)
Destination Interface's assigned role (LAN, WAN, etc.)

The status of the session:
 pass - Application is allowed
 block - Application is blocked (silent)
 reject - Quarantine
 reset - Application is blocked and Reset was sent
Sometimes, there is a block page for blocking
